758245908467_0.png?w=1125 3x\">\n\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/09/19/1758245908467_0.png?w=870 1x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/09/19/1758245908467_0.png?w=1740 2x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/09/19/1758245908467_0.png?w=2610 3x\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/09/19/1758245908467_0.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\">\n\t</picture>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cont-txt\"><h2>국내 유일 스마트 온습도 조절로 <br>쾌적한 숙면</h2><p>습도 조절 휴 시스템, 온도 조절 클리마 시스템은</p><p>한샘만의 독자적인 온습도 조절 기술입니다.</p><p>매트리스 내 쾌적한 수면 환경을 조성하여</p><p>깊은 숙면을 도와줍니다.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div>\n<div class=\"img-box\">\n\t<picture data-origin=\"admin-editor-img\">\n\t\t<source media=\"(max-width:767px)\" srcset=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif?w=750 2x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif?w=1125 3x\">\n\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif?w=870 1x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif?w=1740 2x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif?w=2610 3x\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755152759444_0.gif\" width=\"\" height=\"\">\n\t</picture>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img-box\">\n\t<picture data-origin=\"admin-editor-img\">\n\t\t<source media=\"(max-width:767px)\" srcset=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755158216467_0.gif?w=750 2x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755158216467_0.gif?w=1125 3x\">\n\t\t<source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755158216467_0.gif?w=870 1x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755158216467_0.gif?w=1740 2x, https://image.hanssem.com/hsimg/gds/Editor/2025/08/14/1755158216467_0.gif